data.description:
Welcome to 758 Boenig St,As you approach this charming residence, you'll immediately notice the stately presence of the mature oak trees that adorn the property, casting a tranquil canopy over the home. This natural beauty not only provides a serene backdrop but also offers a cool respite from the Texas sun.Step inside, and you'll discover a spacious and inviting interior, adorned with stunning granite surfaces throughout.A beautifully designed double vanity in the primary bedroom's en-suite bathroom adds an element of luxury and convenience to your daily routine.The primary bedroom also features a walk-in closet, complete with sliding barnyard doors that infuse a touch of rustic charm and modern flair. But that's not all – this home offers outdoor living at its finest with a generous 10x20 deck. Whether you're hosting a summer barbecue, sipping your morning coffee, or stargazing on a clear Texas night, this space provides an ideal backdrop for creating cherished memories.With four bedrooms, this home offers flexibility to suit your lifestyle. The fourth bedroom, with its spacious layout, can be easily transformed into a second living area or a cozy bedroom retreat, allowing you to tailor the space to your specific needs.
Don't miss your chance to make this your forever home – schedule a viewing today and experience the magic of 758 Boenig St for yourself.
